  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently, in a lot of places, datetime  formatting is broken. \r\n\r\nMost of the formatting functions reside in `ui/imports/utils/Utils.qml`. Introduce a new module, `LocaleUtils.qml`, extract the relevant methods from `Utils.qml` and fix them, taking into account default values coming from QML `Locale` and `Date` objects. Options like short/long date formats and 12/24 hour format should be preserved.\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: All\r\n- Operating System: All\r\n\r\n",
